lead_paragraph: New Zealand's Olympic team said they were satisfied with their accommodation for the Rio de Janeiro Games on Sunday, despite their trans-Tasman Sea neighbors Australia refusing to move in.

headline.print_headline: New Zealand Satisfied With Rio Village After Remedial Work
